public class TestSuite
extends TestCase

This class allows collections of TestCase to be grouped together and treated as a single TestCase in accordance with the Composite design pattern.

Note that the concept of testSet does not apply to a TestSuite as a whole. Only individual TestCases have membership (or not) in a particular testSet.
